    "By minimizing the number of trainable parameters required for adaptation, our approach demonstrates a substantial reduction in computational resources while maintaining or even enhancing task performance.",
    "This efficiency is particularly crucial in practical applications, where resource constraints often play a significant role.",
    "Another noteworthy aspect of our study is the extensive evaluation across five different pretrained LLMs: Bloom (7B), Falcon (7B), LLAMA2 (7B), Mistral (7B), and Phi2 (2.7B).",
